title: Av Music Morpher 4.0.60
description:
Av music Morpher Gold 4.0.60

AV Music Morpher Gold is an all-in-one music editor/player helps you cut, copy, paste, edit and mix your songs for remixes, medleys, ringtones, etc. You can now play MP3 stereo music as surround music through your surround speakers and make adjustments in real time easily and visually. It lets you customize a large range of surround sound configurations, supporting 4.0 through 7.1 speakers. The most significant upgrade is the multitrack editor that now helps you edit each track independently on the same waveform chart. With the new multichannel editor, you can edit/morph music, including MP3 surround sound and OGG formats, and edit any number of channels using real-time surround effects and filters. The new Voice Remover-Extractor combines the two most favorite features--Voice Remover and Voice Extractor into one easy-to-use module that helps you do both tasks in a few seconds and in real time. It also includes a powerful CD Burner, and a music organizer.
